      <!-- Project Overview -->
      <section id="overview" class="container mx-auto px-8 py-16">
        <div class="section-header">
          <h2 class="serif text-3xl font-bold text-slate-800">1. Project Overview &amp; Objectives</h2>
        </div>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8 mb-12">
          <div class="lg:col-span-2">
            <h3 class="serif text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 text-slate-800">Core Mission: Implement LIF3 Unified AI Automation Strategy</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-600 mb-6">
              The <strong>core mission of this project is the comprehensive implementation of the LIF3 Unified AI Automation Strategy</strong>. This strategy aims to fundamentally transform the existing financial tracking system into a sophisticated, AI-driven command center. The transformation will involve leveraging advanced artificial intelligence, specifically through the <strong>Model Context Protocol (MCP)</strong>, to enable intelligent decision-making and automate a significant portion of financial tasks.
            </p>

            <div class="pull-quote">
              &#34;The integration of MCP is a critical enabler for this strategy, allowing the AI to dynamically access and utilize external information, thereby enhancing its capabilities beyond static, pre-trained knowledge.&#34;
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-slate-50 p-6 rounded-lg">
            <h4 class="font-semibold mb-4 text-slate-800">Key Objectives</h4>
            <ul class="space-y-3 text-sm text-slate-600">
              <li class="flex items-center">
                <i class="fas fa-check-circle text-green-500 mr-3"></i>
                AI-driven financial command center
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-center">
                <i class="fas fa-check-circle text-green-500 mr-3"></i>
                MCP integration for dynamic data access
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-center">
                <i class="fas fa-check-circle text-green-500 mr-3"></i>
                Unified approach to financial management
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-center">
                <i class="fas fa-check-circle text-green-500 mr-3"></i>
                Accelerated net worth achievement
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="mb-12">
          <h3 class="serif text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 text-slate-800">System Transformation: NestJS/React to Unified Command Center</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-600 mb-6">
            The project entails a <strong>significant system transformation, evolving the current NestJS and React-based financial tracking application into a unified AI-powered command center</strong>. This transformation goes beyond mere feature additions; it involves a fundamental architectural shift to support advanced AI capabilities and seamless data integration.
          </p>

          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mt-8">
            <div class="bg-blue-50 p-6 rounded-lg border-l-4 border-blue-500">
              <h4 class="font-semibold text-blue-800 mb-2">Current State</h4>
              <ul class="text-sm text-blue-700 space-y-1">
                <li>• NestJS backend application</li>
                <li>• React frontend interface</li>
                <li>• Basic financial tracking</li>
                <li>• Manual analysis &amp; decisions</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-green-50 p-6 rounded-lg border-l-4 border-green-500">
              <h4 class="font-semibold text-green-800 mb-2">Future State</h4>
              <ul class="text-sm text-green-700 space-y-1">
                <li>• AI-powered command center</li>
                <li>• MCP integration for data access</li>
                <li>• Predictive analytics &amp; automation</li>
                <li>• Intelligent decision-making</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-slate-800 text-white p-8 rounded-lg">
          <h3 class="serif text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Primary Goal: Accelerate R1,800,000 Net Worth Achievement</h3>
          <p class="mb-4 opacity-90">
            The <strong>primary and quantifiable objective of implementing the LIF3 Unified AI Automation Strategy is to significantly accelerate the achievement of a net worth goal of R1,800,000</strong>. This financial target serves as the central benchmark for the project&#39;s success.
          </p>
          <p class="opacity-90">
            The strategy anticipates that the integration of predictive analytics will provide foresight into market trends and investment performance, while advanced AI automation will streamline financial operations, freeing up resources and capital. The <strong>30% faster goal achievement</strong> directly links the technological advancements to this core financial objective.
          </p>
        </div>
      </section>

