          <div class="mb-12">
            <h3 class="serif text-2xl font-semibold mb-6 text-slate-800">Model Context Protocol (MCP) Integration</h3>

            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
              <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-sm">
                <h4 class="font-semibold mb-4 text-slate-800 flex items-center">
                  <i class="fas fa-network-wired text-blue-500 mr-3"></i>
                  What is MCP?
                </h4>
                <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm mb-4">
                  MCP is an open standard developed by Anthropic, designed to facilitate seamless interaction between AI models and external systems, data sources, and tools.
                </p>
                <ul class="text-sm text-slate-600 space-y-2">
                  <li>• Dynamic context retrieval</li>
                  <li>• Real-time data integration</li>
                  <li>• Standardized query format</li>
                  <li>• Enhanced AI capabilities</li>
                </ul>
              </div>

              <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-sm">
                <h4 class="font-semibold mb-4 text-slate-800 flex items-center">
                  <i class="fas fa-cogs text-green-500 mr-3"></i>
                  Implementation Benefits
                </h4>
                <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm mb-4">
                  MCP will enable the AI command center to access real-time financial data, market information, and user-specific details for intelligent decision-making.
                </p>
                <ul class="text-sm text-slate-600 space-y-2">
                  <li>• Live market data feeds</li>
                  <li>• External API integration</li>
                  <li>• Dynamic context awareness</li>
                  <li>• Enhanced predictive accuracy</li>
                </ul>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

